Zync,is,a,global,messaging,platform,that,provides,communication,methods,over,SMS,Voice,Email,and,Fax,Its,SMS,platform,focuses,on,long,code,and,selects,the,most,reliable,routes,using,a,global,prefix,lookup,The,voice,platform,comes,with,direct,connectors,to,every,major,geographic,region,The,fax,engine,is,capable,of,delivering,and,receiving,millions,of,pages,per,day,All,of,Zync,s,messaging,functions,are,designed,to,send,and,receive,messages,to,and,from,anywhere,in,the,world